</div></div></div> <div class="bs-advance-accordion__right-container">  <div id="accordion_62cf60dc96e6"><div class="card active">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_0b05a038952b_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_0b05a038952b"
        aria-expanded="true"
        aria-controls="panel_0b05a038952b"><h3>Advanced Listening</div><div
                    id="panel_0b05a038952b"
                    class="collapse show "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_0b05a038952b_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_62cf60dc96e6"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>Speak naturally — with SoundHound’s leading voice recognition, our AI agents understand you no matter your accent, tempo, or background noise. No scripts. No frustration. Just real conversations.</p>
      </div>  </div></div><div class="card ">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_d498f5a02fee_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_d498f5a02fee"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="panel_d498f5a02fee"><h3>Fluid &amp; Adaptable</div><div
                    id="panel_d498f5a02fee"
                    class="collapse  "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_d498f5a02fee_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_62cf60dc96e6"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>No more dead ends. Amelia uses generative conversation and autonomous reasoning to converse with you like it’s person-to-person, and adapts on the fly.</p>
      </div>  </div></div><div class="card ">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_136dfd4f43d3_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_136dfd4f43d3"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="panel_136dfd4f43d3"><h3>Talk Across Channels</div><div
                    id="panel_136dfd4f43d3"
                    class="collapse  "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_136dfd4f43d3_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_62cf60dc96e6"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>You can choose how to interact with Amelia and can even switch between talking and texting — all within the same conversation. Whatever feels natural.</p>
      </div>  </div></div><div class="card ">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_867bb2887827_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_867bb2887827"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="panel_867bb2887827"><h3>Complete Tasks</div><div
                    id="panel_867bb2887827"
                    class="collapse  "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_867bb2887827_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_62cf60dc96e6"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>Amelia turns conversations into actions — resetting passwords, processing returns, and more — to enhance customer interactions.</p>
      </div>  </div></div><div class="card ">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_1a37b247d2be_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_1a37b247d2be"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="panel_1a37b247d2be"><h3>Always On Brand</div><div
                    id="panel_1a37b247d2be"
                    class="collapse  "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_1a37b247d2be_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_62cf60dc96e6"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>Customize Amelia to match your brand — from designing your AI agent’s tone, voice, and appearance, to putting guardrails around what they do and say.</p>
      </div>  </div></div>      </div>  </div></div>


<div class="wp-block-e25m-div bs-div bs-div-0489a513e7ee6e770a714cb82478926a84b8ac1e bs-div---default"><div class="bs-div__inner d-flex    ">
