                            <figure class='figure justify-content-start d-flex'>
                            <picture>
                            
                            <img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class='img-fluid'   alt='a 3D graph showing increase in revenue' title=''  data-lazy-src="https://www.soundhound.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Analytics-v2.jpg" /><noscript><img src='https://www.soundhound.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Analytics-v2.jpg' class='img-fluid'   alt='a 3D graph showing increase in revenue' title=''  /></noscript>
                            </picture>
                                
                            </figure>
                        </div></div></div></div> <div class="bs-advance-accordion__right-container">  <div id="accordion_c998513f428d"><div class="card active">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_4812d1ee3d01_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_4812d1ee3d01"
        aria-expanded="true"
        aria-controls="panel_4812d1ee3d01"><h3>AI Agents</div><div
                    id="panel_4812d1ee3d01"
                    class="collapse show "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_4812d1ee3d01_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_c998513f428d"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>AI Agents is your workspace for designing, testing, and deploying conversational agents who take action. Our Agentic+ framework orchestrates agents through advanced LLM‑driven reasoning.</p>
      </div>  </div></div><div class="card ">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_f171b9ebefef_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_f171b9ebefef"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="panel_f171b9ebefef"><h3>Answers</div><div
                    id="panel_f171b9ebefef"
                    class="collapse  "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_f171b9ebefef_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_c998513f428d"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>Answers is the central hub to unify your enterprise knowledge and fine tune AI responses. Powered by RAG and advanced LLMs, this rich tool delivers precise, context‑aware responses every time.</p>
      </div>  </div></div><div class="card ">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_2b6edcfb64d1_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_2b6edcfb64d1"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="panel_2b6edcfb64d1"><h3>Contact Center</div><div
                    id="panel_2b6edcfb64d1"
                    class="collapse  "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_2b6edcfb64d1_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_c998513f428d"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>Contact Center is the command hub for every AI‑escalated hand‑off. Configure escalation teams and queues, monitor live conversations, and equip reps with response templates — all in one place.</p>
      </div>  </div></div><div class="card ">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_401a5ebba44f_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_401a5ebba44f"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="panel_401a5ebba44f"><h3>Agent Console</div><div
                    id="panel_401a5ebba44f"
                    class="collapse  "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_401a5ebba44f_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_c998513f428d"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>Agent Console gives every rep a real‑time AI copilot to deliver the best customer result — surfacing insights, suggestions, and next‑best actions right inside the live conversation.</p>
      </div>  </div></div><div class="card ">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_643d1f957b92_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_643d1f957b92"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="panel_643d1f957b92"><h3>Learning</div><div
                    id="panel_643d1f957b92"
                    class="collapse  "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_643d1f957b92_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_c998513f428d"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>Learning turns every conversation into a feedback loop for rapid improvement. Track intent and resolution rates, pinpoint friction, and refine AI‑generated escalation flows within one dashboard.</p>
      </div>  </div></div><div class="card ">  <div class="card-header accordion__block__btn " id="panel_624c1ece6928_header"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#panel_624c1ece6928"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="panel_624c1ece6928"><span>Analytics</div><div
                    id="panel_624c1ece6928"
                    class="collapse  "
                    aria-labelledby="panel_624c1ece6928_header"
                    data-parent="#accordion_c998513f428d"
                ><div class="card-body">
<p>Analytics illuminates each interaction — AI or human — so you can optimize with confidence. Replay full conversation flows, track NPS factors, and gauge answer accuracy for a deeper QA.</p>
      </div>  </div></div>      </div>  </div></div>


