<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center">The possibility of GenAI meets the needs of Enterprise.</h2>



<div class="wp-block-e25m-row bs-row row  bs-row---default">
<div class=" bs-column col-sm-12  col-lg-0 col-md-6   bs-column-4421becea4b2ba94a16e419536e720e7a19bf92a bs-column---default bs-column--play-audio-gap     ">
<div class="bs-card "><div class="bs-card__container 
				
				"><div class="bs-card__image"><figure><picture><img decoding="async" class="none img-fluid" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" data-lazy-src="https://www.soundhound.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Answer-Guardrails.jpg"/><noscript><img decoding="async" class="none img-fluid" src="https://www.soundhound.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Answer-Guardrails.jpg" alt=""/></noscript></picture></figure></div><div class="bs-card__title"><h3>Answer Guardrails</h3></div><div class="bs-card__description"><p>Our conversational AI agents enable trustworthy, context-aware interactions, blending seamless self-service with enterprise-grade security and smooth escalation to human agents.</p></div></div></div>
</div>



<div class=" bs-column col-sm-12  col-lg-0 col-md-6   bs-column-4421becea4b2ba94a16e419536e720e7a19bf92a bs-column---default bs-column--play-audio-gap     ">
<div class="bs-card "><div class="bs-card__container 
				
				"><div class="bs-card__image"><figure><picture><img decoding="async" class="none img-fluid" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" data-lazy-src="https://www.soundhound.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Hallucinations.jpg"/><noscript><img decoding="async" class="none img-fluid" src="https://www.soundhound.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Hallucinations.jpg" alt=""/></noscript></picture></figure></div><div class="bs-card__title"><h3>Hallucination Control</h3></div><div class="bs-card__description"><p>Our AI agents are grounded in data from your systems — never guessing. Layered guardrails, confidence checks, safe fallbacks, and human escalation keep responses trustworthy at scale.</p></div></div></div>
</div>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-e25m-row bs-row row  bs-row---default">
<div class=" bs-column col-sm-12  col-lg-0 col-md-6   bs-column-4421becea4b2ba94a16e419536e720e7a19bf92a bs-column---default bs-column--play-audio-gap     ">
<div class="bs-card "><div class="bs-card__container 
				
