<div class=" bs-column col-sm-12  col-lg-0 col-md-6   bs-column-4421becea4b2ba94a16e419536e720e7a19bf92a bs-column---default bs-column--play-audio-gap     ">
<div class="bs-card "><div class="bs-card__container 
				
				"><div class="bs-card__image"><figure><picture><img decoding="async" class="none img-fluid" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" data-lazy-src="https://www.soundhound.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/System-Agnostic.jpg"/><noscript><img decoding="async" class="none img-fluid" src="https://www.soundhound.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/System-Agnostic.jpg" alt=""/></noscript></picture></figure></div><div class="bs-card__title"><h3>Systems Agnostic</h3></div><div class="bs-card__description"><p>We’re systems agnostic by design, with an ever-growing integrations library that connects across your existing stack. Everything is fully customizable and fits your needs.</p></div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></section>



