<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-left" style="font-size:32px"><strong>Analysts recognize</strong> <strong>us as a leader.</strong></h2>



<p class="has-text-align-left">See what leading industry experts say about SoundHound AI’s Amelia platform.</p>
</div>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-e25m-row bs-row row  bs-row---default">
<div class=" bs-column col-sm-12   bs-column-5f6574ebb29ac8d58ab608d2aff5b1bbe4f96332 bs-column---default     "><div id="slider-de34cb617e37aa41b422d7c32ec128487d52ea5d"
